20junction%20of%20two%20tectonic%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%207.6-magnitude%20jolt%20hit%20Taiwan%20in%20September%201999%2C%20killing%20around%202%2C400%20people%20in%20the%20deadliest%20natural%20disaster%20in%20the%20island's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20experiences%20around%201%2C500%20jolts%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20are%20mild%2C%20although%20the%20damage%20they%20cause%20varies%20according%20to%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20epicentre%20below%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20and%20its%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20severity%20of%20tsunamis%20--%20vast%20and%20potentially%20destructive%20series%20of%20waves%20that%20can%20move%20at%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20(kilometres)%20per%20hour%20--%20also%20depends%20upon%20multiple%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20larger%20quakes%20usually%20cause%20little%20damage%20in%20Japan%20and%20Taiwan%20thanks%20to%20special%20construction%20techniques%20and%20strict%20building%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20also%20developed%20sophisticated%20procedures%20and%20technology%20to%20alert%20and%20evacuate%20people%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20biggest%20earthquake%20on%20record%20was%20a%20massive%209.0-magnitude%20undersea%20jolt%20in%20March%202011%20off%20Japan's%20northeast%20coast%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20tsunami%20that%20left%20around%2018%2C500%20people%20dead%20or%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202011%20catastrophe%20also%20sent%20three%20reactors%20into%20meltdown%20at%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant%2C%20causing%20Japan's%20worst%20post-war%20disaster%20and%20the%20most%20serious%20nuclear%20accident%20since%20Chernobyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20cost%20was%20estimated%20at%2016.9%20trillion%20yen%20(%24112%20billion)%2C%20not%20including%20for%20the%20hazardous%20decommissioning%20of%20the%20Fukushima%20facility%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20stricter%20building%20guidelines%2C%20many%20structures%2C%20particularly%20outside%20major%20cities%2C%20but%20not%20only%20there%2C%20are%20old%20and%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20brought%20home%20in%20the%207.5-magnitude%20New%20Year's%20Day%20quake%20in%202024%2C%20which%20hit%20Noto%20Peninsula%20and%20killed%20more%20than%20230%20people%2C%20many%20of%20them%20when%20older%20buildings%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712106840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fdsol0vmg_taiwan-earthquake-_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F7-5-magnitude-earthquake-hits-taiwan-japan-issues-tsunami-alert-5363594%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20major%20earthquake%20hit%20Taiwan's%20east%20shortly%20before%208%3A00%20am%20(0000%20GMT)%20local%20time%20Wednesday%2C%20prompting%20tsunami%20warnings%20for%20the%20self-ruled%20island%20as%20well%20as%20parts%20of%20southern%20Japan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F7-5-magnitude-earthquake-hits-taiwan-japan-issues-tsunami-alert-5363594%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F7-5-magnitude-earthquake-hits-taiwan-japan-issues-tsunami-alert-5363594%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F7-5-magnitude-earthquake-hits-taiwan-japan-issues-tsunami-alert-5363594%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Strongest%20earthquake%20in%2025%20years%20hits%20Taiwan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712106764000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0E83%2Fproduction%2F_115651730_breaking-promo-976.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww