h%20them%20to%20their%20leader's%20house%20in%20Faridabad's%20Sanjay%20Enclave.%20The%20video%20from%20outside%20Bajrangi's%20house%20shows%20the%20cow%20vigilante%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20member%2C%20holding%20a%20stick%20as%20other%20men%20from%20his%20group%20drag%20a%20pleading%20Shamu%20along%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20policeman%20is%20seen%20sitting%20on%20a%20chair%20inches%20from%20the%20man%20and%20he%20gets%20up%2C%20but%20does%20nothing%20to%20intervene.%20A%20man%20can%20then%20be%20heard%20asking%20the%20others%20to%20turn%20Shamu%20on%20his%20side%20and%20Bajrangi%20alias%20Raj%20Kumar%20proceeds%20to%20hit%20him%20with%20a%20stick%20at%20least%20four%20times.%20Police%20officials%20said%20the%20mother%20of%20one%20of%20the%20girls%20had%20also%20hit%20Shamu%20with%20the%20stick%20before%20Bajrangi%20proceeded%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20in%20charge%20of%20Saran%20Police%20Station%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20the%20viral%20video%20and%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20man%20who%20was%20beaten%20up.%20After%20we%20get%20a%20complaint%20from%20him%2C%20we%20will%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20If%20we%20don't%20get%20a%20complaint%20from%20him%2C%20we%20will%20track%20down%20the%20accused%20using%20the%20video%20and%20social%20media%20and%20take%20action%20against%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20communal%20violence%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh%20had%20broken%20out%20in%20July%20last%20year%20during%20a%20procession%20organised%20by%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20then%20spread%20to%20other%20areas%2C%20including%20Gurugram%20and%20Badshahpur.%20Five%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20at%20least%2070%20people%20were%20injured.%20A%20mosque%20had%20also%20been%20set%20ablaze%20and%20a%20cleric%20was%20among%20the%20dead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712106060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fiaad1t58_bittu-bajrangi-beats-man-with-sti