oopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%228748b1f4b0f53a7855ea4e1930f38065%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.staralliance.com%2Fen%2Fstar-lounge-detail%3FloungeDetailsForAirport%3DLAX%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStar%20Alliance%20Lounge%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20lounge%2C%20which%20caters%20to%20first-class%20and%20business-class%20international%20travelers%20as%20well%20as%20some%20credit-card%20holders%2C%20was%20another%20new%20experience.%20Before%20landing%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairport-lounge-features-food-alcohol-crowded-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20had%20never%20stepped%20inside%20an%20airport%20lounge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20I%20had%20a%20seven-hour%20layover%20in%20LA%20to%20discover%20its%20unexpected%20perks.%20I%20spent%20hours%20tasting%20every%20food%20item%20I%20could%20get%20my%20hands%20on%20and%20explored%20the%20lounge's%20outdoor%20patio%20and%20quiet%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20free%20alcohol%20around%20every%20corner.%20But%20my%20favorite%20perk%20was%20knowing%20that%20a%20representative%20from%20Air%20New%20Zealand%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20lounge%20supplying%20flight%20updates.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20stress%20about%20missing%20an%20announcement%20or%20my%20flight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20lounge%20to%20be%20a%20luxe%20respite%20and%20much%20nicer%20than%20the%20airport%20gates%20and%20restaurants%20I%20typically%20camp%20at%20during%20layovers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20it%20was%20time%20to%20board%20the%20flight%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20to%20walk%20onto%20the%20plane.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Insider's%20author%20entered%20a%20nearly%20empty%20jet%20bridge%20when%20she%20boarded%20the%20Air%20New%20Zealand%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63bdcb4106706e0019a9ad4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20author%20entered%20a%20nearly%20empty%20jet%20bridge%20when%20she%20boarded%20the%20Air%20New%20Zealand%20flight.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20full%20stomach%2C%20I%20left%20the%20airport%20lounge%2C%20grabbed%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-carry-on-bag%5C%22%3Ecarry-on%20suitcase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20navigated%20through%20the%20crowds%20of%20people%20waiting%20to%20board%20the%20flight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20gate%2C%20I%20passed%20families%20and%20couples%20waiting%20for%20their%20boarding%20groups%20to%20be%20called%20while%20my%20group%20%E2%80%94%20business%20class%2C%20which%20is%20the%20airline's%20version%20of%20first%20class%20%E2%80%94%20was%20welcome%20to%20step%20onto%20the%20plane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reached%20the%20jet%20bridge%20entrance%2C%20scanned%20my%20boarding%20pass%2C%20and%20joined%20two%20dozen%20business-class%20passengers.%20Together%2C%20we%20were%20some%20of%20the%20first%20passengers%20on%20the%20plane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20only%20ever%20sat%20in%20economy%2C%20boarding%20first%20was%20an%20entirely%20new%20experience.%20I'm%20typically%20one%20of%20the%20last%20people%20on%20the%20plane%20and%20accustomed%20to%20hunting%20for%20rare%20overhead%20luggage%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20were%20fewer%20people%2C%20the%20business-class%20cabin%20felt%20more%20spacious.%20I%20had%20plenty%20of%20overhead%20storage%20available%20in%20business%20class%20for%20all%20my%20belongings%20with%20no%20worry%20of%20being%20told%20I'd%20need%20to%20gate%20check%20a%20bag.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20knew%20to%20expect%20more%20space%20in%20business%20class%2C%20but%20my%20seat%20exceeded%20my%20dreams.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20business-class%20section%20on%20Air%20New%20Zealand's%20Boeing%20777-300ER%20planes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62d83e7a0c98f500195eb220%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20business-class%20section%20on%20Air%20New%20Zealand's%20Boeing%20777-300ER%20planes.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20perks%20of%20flying%20business%20class%20on%20long-haul%20flights%20is%20the%20extra%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20economy%2C%20I'm%20used%20to%20cramped%20seats%20that%20hardly%20recline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20an%20expectation%20of%20a%20larger%20seat%20with%20more%20room%20in%20business%20class%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20by%20how%20spacious%20the%20seat%20actually%20felt%20on%20my%20Air%20New%20Zealand%20flight.%20In%20front%20of%20me%20was%20a%20footrest%2C%20where%20at%205%20feet%20and%208%20inches%2C%20I%20could%20stretch%20out%20my%20legs.%20I%20also%20used%20this%20space%20to%20store%20my%20backpack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tray%20table%20was%20larger%20than%20any%20I've%20seen%20in%20economy.%20But%20perhaps%20the%20biggest%20added%20bonus%20of%20my%20seat%20was%20that%20it%20didn't%20just%20recline%20a%20few%20inches%20like%20economy%20seats%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20had%20four%20buttons%20to%20experiment%20with%20moving%20my%20seat%20backwards%20and%20forwards.%20Plus%2C%20I%20could%20fully%20lie%20flat%2C%20which%20would%20be%20useful%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20go%20to%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20and%20before%20economy%20class%20had%20finished%20boarding%2C%20I%20was%20alr