p%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20surprised%20to%20see%20a%20blanket%20and%20pillow%20waiting%20for%20me%20at%20my%20seat%20since%20I've%20had%20those%20amenities%20in%20economy%20before.%20But%20I%20was%20thrilled%20to%20find%20a%20bag%20of%20complimentary%20toiletries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purple%20pouch%20contained%20a%20toothbrush%2C%20toothpaste%2C%20mouthwash%2C%20ear%20plugs%2C%20an%20eye%20mask%2C%20lip%20balm%2C%20lotion%2C%20a%20pen%2C%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20socks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20lathered%20the%C2%A0balm%20across%20my%20lips%2C%20I%20wondered%20how%20much%20the%20tube%20cost.%20I%20later%20found%20out%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.ashleyandco.co%2Fproducts%2Flip-punch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAshley%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20Lip%20Punch%3C%2Fa%3E%20retails%20for%20%2415%20and%20the%20brand's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.ashleyandco.co%2F%23soothe-tube%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESoothe%20Tube%20lotion%3C%2Fa%3E%20costs%20%2425.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20small%20perks%20added%20an%20element%20of%20luxury%20throughout%20the%20flight%2C%20and%20they%20came%20in%20handy%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20left%20my%20toothpaste%20in%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20carry-on%20suitcase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20thought%20airline%20courtesy%20meant%20never%20taking%20off%20your%20shoes.%20But%20before%20the%20plane%20left%20the%20jet%20bridge%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20nearly%20everyone's%20shoes%20in%20business%20class%20were%20already%20off.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20two%20passengers%20across%20from%20the%20author%20had%20their%20shoes%20off%20shortly%20after%20boarding%20the%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63bd9b5606706e0019a9a107%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%