20dinner%2C%20flight%20attendants%20stopped%20at%20each%20seat%20to%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20bed.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20flight%20was%20a%20red-eye.%20We%20departed%20Los%20Angeles%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20were%20scheduled%20to%20land%20in%20Auckland%20in%20the%20early%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%20was%20cleared%2C%20passengers%20slowly%20retreated%20to%20the%20bathroom%20to%20freshen%20up%20before%20bedtime.%20I%20headed%20to%20the%20restroom%20to%20brush%20my%20teeth%20and%20wash%20my%20face.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20was%20done%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20had%20converted%20my%20seat%20into%20a%20bed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20perks%20of%20business%20class%20on%20Air%20New%20Zealand's%20long-haul%20flights%20is%20that%20the%20seats%20transform%20into%20lie-flat%20beds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20turn-down%20service%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20presses%20a%20few%20buttons%2C%20which%20turns%20the%20upright%20seat%20into%20a%20horizontal%20bed.%20Then%2C%20they%20add%20a%20mattress%20topper%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20blanket%20and%20pillow.%20Finally%2C%20they%20pull%20out%20the%20seat%20belts%20for%20safety%20and%20check%20in%20with%20each%20passenger%20to%20see%20if%20they%20want%20any%20final%20drinks%2C%20snacks%2C%20or%20items%20before%20dimming%20the%20cabin%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20the%20transition%20from%20dinner%20to%20sleep%20was%20effortless%20for%20passengers.%20As%20I%20grabbed%20my%20eye%20mask%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20odds%20I'd%20fall%20asleep%20were%20high.%20I%20rarely%20have%20that%20confidence%20when%20I'm%20sitting%20upright%20on%20a%20plane%20in%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20sure%20enough%2C%20I%20slept%20for%20about%20five%20hours%20in%20the%20comfy%20bed.%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20smell%20of%20hot%20coffee%20and%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20eating%2C%20I%20retreated%20back%20