20to%20address%20four%20units%2C%20so%20both%20of%20them%20were%20going%20on%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20get%20over%20the%20hump%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20deal%20to%20buy%20this%20other%20house%20had%20fallen%20apart%2C%20and%20I%20just%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20I%20should%20be%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20tenant%20upstairs%20and%20I%20weren't%20comfortable.%20We%20didn't%20know%20what%20the%20situation%20might%20be.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20scenarios%20that%20could%20happen%20with%20whoever%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20owner%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20because%20I%20was%20on%20a%20month-to-month%20lease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20could%20have%20asked%20me%20to%20move%20out%20so%20that%20they%20could%20take%20the%20place%2C%20or%20they%20could%20have%20raised%20my%20rent.%20I%20was%20paying%20way%20under%20market%20value%20for%20the%20rent.%20When%20I%20first%20moved%20in%2C%20my%20rent%20was%20%24750%2C%20and%20about%20two%20years%20in%2C%20my%20landlord%20raised%20it%20only%20around%20%2450%20more.%20Especially%20having%20a%20kid%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20very%20stable%20situation%20to%20be%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20decided%20to%20make%20an%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20was%20accepted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20had%20become%20a%20real-estate%20agent%2C%20so%20she%20was%20the%20one%20helping%20me%20out%20through%20all%20this.%20She%20kept%20bugging%20me%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20you%20should%20do%20this.%20You're%20already%20living%20in%20this%20house%20and%20we%20know%20the%20tenant%20upstairs.%20If%20we%20put%20in%20a%20decent%20offer%2C%20I%20think%20we%20could%20really%20knock%20this%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20posing%20for%20a%20picture%20with%20their%20daughter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660b195516bde8d4ead459bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%