20military%20veterans%20and%20public-service%20veterans.%20The%20program%20offered%20a%20mortgage%20discount%20rate%2C%20so%20whatever%20rate%20I%20had%20initially%2C%20they%20would%20buy%20down%20a%20point%20for%20me%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20%240%20down.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20move.%20I%20now%20own%20a%20duplex%20with%20a%20tenant%20upstairs%2C%20who%20I%20have%20a%20great%20relationship%20with.%20I%20have%20this%20one-year%20home%20warranty.%20I%20hit%20the%20ground%20running%20on%20this%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAfter%20four%20years%20of%20living%20here%2C%20I%20can%20finally%20make%20it%20my%20own%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20house%20closed%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20feel%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20still%2C%20to%20this%20moment%2C%20kind%20of%20scared.%20It's%20a%20big%20jump%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20very%20exciting%20feeling%20knowing%20that%20everything%20fell%20the%20way%20it%20was%20supposed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspecially%20with%20a%20kid%2C%20too.%20She's%20six%20and%20in%20kindergarten.%20Having%20to%20move%20and%20possibly%20change%20schools%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20mid-school%20year.%20So%20that%20was%20a%20big%20relief%20off%20of%20my%20shoulders%20%E2%80%94%20to%20know%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20do%20all%20that%20and%20put%20my%20daughter%20through%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20taking%20a%20selfie%20in%20a%20mirror%20with%20his%20daughter%20on%20his%20shoulders.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660b18eb1caec1275a6b9ada%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGuerra%20and%20his%20daughter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dom%20Guerra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20so%20very%20grateful%20for%20the%20way%20it%20played%20out%20and%20excited%20that%20it%20didn't%20have%20to%20mean%20moving.%20My%20stuff%20is%20here%2C%20and%20now%20I%20can%20make%20it%20mine.%20I%20can%20paint%20or