now%20that%20you're%20the%20guy%20who's%20paying%20the%20mortgage%20and%20the%20property%20taxes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20that.%20And%20with%20elections%20coming%20up%2C%20there%20are%20tax%20levies%20on%20the%20board%20that%20may%20affect%20your%20payments.%20It's%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20one%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20getting%20the%20keys%20and%20making%20cash%20flow%20off%20of%20this%20property.%20I%20knew%20right%20from%20the%20gate%20that%20that%20was%20not%20going%20to%20be%20the%20situation.%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20would%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20with%20every%20appliance%20that%20runs%20both%20my%20unit%20and%20the%20upstairs%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20of%20everything%20for%20the%20entire%20house.%20There's%20not%20just%20one%20water%20heater%2C%20there's%20two.%20I%20don't%20have%20one%20furnace%2C%20I%20have%20two.%20I%20have%20a%20washer%20and%20dryer%20set%2C%20and%20there's%20another%20one%20for%20the%20person%20upstairs%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20upstairs%20tenant%20is%20such%20a%20great%20guy.%20He's%20very%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20me%20and%20even%20take%20on%20some%20of%20the%20load%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20help%20you%20here%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20to%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20guy%20who's%20very%20knowledgeable%20and%20knows%20more%20than%20me%2C%20so%20I%20take%20that%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20listen%20the%20entire%20way%20and%20help.%20I'm%20learning%20everything%20from%20all%20my%20resources%20around%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EInitially%2C%20my%20goal%20wasn't%20to%20make%20money%2C%20but%20I%20might%20buy%20another%20duplex%20in%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20it%20a%20cash-flow%20asset.%20If%20the%20market%20changes%20and%20falls%20more%20to%20the%20buyer%20side%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20try%20to%20repeat%20the%20cycle%20again%3A%20Buy%20another%20duplex%2C%20