20from%20flying%20anywhere%20near%20bad%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20formal%20lifting%20of%20the%20F-35A%20lightning%20standoff%20restriction%20was%20released%20on%20March%2019%2C%26quot%3B%20F-35%20Joint%20Program%20Office%20spokesperson%20Russell%20Goemaere%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20News%20of%20this%20change%20was%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2024%2F04%2Fexclusive-pentagon-clears-f-35-to-fly-in-lightning-after-years-long-hold%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Breaking%20Defense%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restriction%2C%20which%20had%20prohibited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftest-pilot-f-35-demands-more-than-great-flying-skills-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-35A%2C%20the%20conventional%20takeoff%20and%20landing%20variant%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20flying%20within%2025%20miles%20of%20lightning%20since%20June%202020%2C%20was%20lifted%20after%20a%20major%20fix%20to%20the%20aircraft's%20On-Board%20Inert%20Gas%20Generation%20System%2C%20or%20OBIGGS.%20Goemaere%20said%20the%20fix%20included%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20robust%26quot%3B%20OBIGGS%20hardware%20design%2C%20as%20well%20as%20software%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OBIGGS%20is%20designed%20to%20replace%20combustible%20gas%20in%20the%20jet's%20fuel%20tank%2C%20such%20as%20oxygen%2C%20with%20material%2C%20in%20this%20case%20nitrogen-enriched%20air%2C%20that%20won't%20ignite%20or%20explode.%20Protection%20systems%20are%20intended%20to%20prevent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarines-order-lightning-rods-to-keep-their-f-35s-from-getting-fried-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elightning%20from%20frying%20the%20aircraft's%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20starting%20an%20onboard%20fire%2C%20or%2C%20in%20the%20obvious%20worst%20case%2C%20a%20catastrophic%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesting%20for%20these%20efforts%20was%20a%20combination%20of%20lab%20and%20flight%20testing%2C%26quot%3B%20Goemaere%20added%2C%20noting%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fix%20restores%20operational%20capability%2C%20while%20providing%20additional%20safety%20for%20the%20pilots%20and%20aircraft.%26quot%3B%20He%20declined%20to%20go%20into%20specific%20detail%20or%20the%20number%20of%20aircraft%20modified%20or%20in%20the%20modification%20process%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20operational%20security%20concerns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-35%20aircraft%20mechanic%20with%20Marine%20Fighter%20Attack%20Squadron%20(VMFA)%20542%20and%20an%20F-35B%20instructor%20pilot%20with%20Marine%20Fighter%20Attack%20Training%20Squadron%20(VMFAT)%20501%20perform%20preflight%20checks%20on%20an%20F-35B%20Lightning%20II%20jet%20at%20Marine%20Corps%20Air%20Station%20Cherry%20Point%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20April%2020%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6508c8e912dc4f001a15fc2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-35%20aircraft%20mechanic%20with%20Marine%20Fighter%20Attack%20Squadron%20(VMFA)%20542%20and%20an%20F-35B%20instructor%20pilot%20with%20Marine%20Fighter%20Attack%20Training%20Squadron%20(VMFAT)%20501%20perform%20preflight%20checks%20on%20an%20F-35B%20Lightning%20II%20jet%20at%20Marine%20Corps%20Air%20Station%20Cherry%20Point%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20April%2020%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EUS%20Marine%20Corps%2FStaff%20Sgt.%20Theodore%20Bergan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20problems%20with%20the%20F-35's%20fuel%20tank%20inerting%20system%20have%20been%20trouble%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-f-35b-grounded-exploding-lightning-fuel-tank-2013-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoD%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20these%20issues%20since%20at%20least%202009%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20was%20highlighted%20in%20an%20operational%20test%20and%20evaluation%20report%20a%20few%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202012%20report%20said%20%26quot%3Btests%20of%20the%20fuel%20tank%20inerting%20system%20in%202009%20identified%20deficiencies%20in%20maintaining%20the%20required%20lower%20fuel%20tank%20oxygen%20levels%20to%20prevent%20fuel%20tank%20explosions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20system%2C%20%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20able%20to%20maintain%20fuel%20tank%20inerting%20through%20some%20critical%20portions%20of%20a%20simulated%20mission%20profile.%20The%20program%20is%20redesigning%20the%20On-Board%20Inert%20Gas%20Generating%20System%20(OBIGGS)%20to%20provide%20the%20required%20levels%20of%20protection%20from%20threat%20and%20from%20fuel%20tank%20explosions%20induced%20by%20lightning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20reports%20indicated%20that%20the%20F-35%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff35-fighters-mission-capable-just-over-half-the-time-watchdog-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20staggeringly%20expensive%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20had%20to%20overcome%20a%20number%20of%20problems%2C%20had%20made%20progress%20on%20the%20issue%20following%20a%20rework.%20Flying%20restrictions%20were%20lifted%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20in%202020%2C%20additional%20problems%20were%20discovered.%20The%20aim%20was%20that%20the%20restrictions%20could%20be%20lifted%20in%202022%2C%20but%20more%20deficiencies%20were%20found%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20variants%20of%20this%20jet%2C%20the%20F-35B%20short%20takeoff%20and%20vertical%20landing%20variant%20and%20F-35C%20carrier-based%20fighter%2C%20haven't%20had%20the%20exact%20same%20issues%20with%20lightning%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-all-the-problems-with-the-f-35-that-the-pentagon-found-in-a-2014-report-2015-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproblems%3C