%20million%20it%20has%20reportedly%20spent%20appealing%20for%20votes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0particularly%20those%20of%20retail%20investors%2C%20who%20hold%20about%2040%25%20of%20Disney's%20shares%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-stock-pinocchio-iger-peltz-trian-activist-investing-proxy-fight-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20has%20run%20extensive%20ad%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20featuring%20characters%20like%20Pinocchio%20and%20Donald%20Duck's%20uncle%2C%20Ludwig%20Von%20Drake.%20Iger%20and%20other%20executives%20have%20spent%20weeks%20meeting%20with%20and%20calling%20major%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Disney%20wasn't%20concerned%20about%20losing%20one%20or%20two%20board%20seats%20here%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20as%20aggressive%20and%20public%20about%20pushing%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Schloetzer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrian%2C%20too%2C%20has%20spent%20eight%20figures%20on%20its%20campaign%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftrian-issues-white-paper-on-the-walt-disney-company-1033130152%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublishing%20white%20papers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20taking%20to%20social%20media%20with%20satirical%20animations%20of%20Disney's%20cast%20of%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20been%20paying%20off.%20On%20Monday%2C%20institutional%20investors%20Neuberger%20Berman%20and%20the%20California%20Public%20Employees'%20Retirement%20System%20threw%20their%20support%20behind%20Trian%2C%20which%20controls%20about%201.8%25%20of%20Disney%20shares%2C%20most%20of%20them%20belonging%20to%20disgruntled%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freclusive-rich-billionaires-list-secretive-perlmutter-anschultz-mars-barclay-wertheimer-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarvel%20chairman%20Ike%20Perlmutter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20proxy%20advisory%20firm%20Institutional