aced%20on%20a%20debt%20watch%20list%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20his%20Axos%20Bank%20investment%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Trump's%20bond.%20Axos%20Bank%20CEO%20Greg%20Garrabrants%20has%20previously%20donated%20around%20%2450%2C000%20to%20Republican%20campaigns%20since%202012%2C%20with%20%249%2C600%20in%20support%20of%20Trump%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fec.gov%2Fdata%2Freceipts%2Findividual-contributions%2F%3Fcontributor_name%3DGregory%2BGarrabrants%26max_date%3D12%252F31%252F2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20elections%20records%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHankey's%20net%20worth%20is%20estimated%20at%20%247.4%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fprofile%2Fdon-hankey%2F%3Fsh%3D2ba84a081783%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20nearly%20doubled%20within%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHankey%20grew%20up%20a%20lot%20worker%2C%20washing%20and%20polishing%20cars%2C%20and%20later%20held%20a%20job%20as%20a%20salesman%20at%20his%20father's%20Ford%20dealership%2C%20which%20he%20fully%20acquired%20in%201972%20and%20built%20his%20empire%20from%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Blittle-known%20king%20of%20subprime%20car%20loans%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20Forbes%20profile%2C%20his%20largest%20venture%2C%20Westlake%20Financial%20Services%2C%20operates%20as%20a%20subprime%20financing%20company%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hankeygroup.com%2Fcompanies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworth%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2416.8%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hankey%20Group%20website.%20Westlake%20collaborates%20with%20car%20dealerships%20nationwide%20to%20offer%20loans%20to%20people%20with%20poor%20or%20nonexistent%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20also%20owns%20a%20real%20estate%20firm%2C%20Hankey%20Investment%20Company%20LP.%20The%20company%20owns%20488%2C3