st-friendly%20than%20the%20chemical-based%20foaming%20agents%20available%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGOBAiR%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20Professor%20Sandeep%20Chaudhary%20and%20his%20PhD%20student%20Sanchit%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20working%20on%20ways%20and%20means%20to%20generate%20higher%20incomes%20from%20cow%20dung%20and%20support%20%3Cem%3Egaushalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cowsheds)%20in%20managing%20stray%20cattle.%20This%20is%20how%20GOBAiR%20came%20into%20existence%2C%26quot%3B%20Professor%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20GOBAiR%20enables%20lightweight%20concrete%2C%20which%20can%20be%20produced%20at%20about%2024%25%20lower%20cost%20than%20commercially%20used%20building%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20product%20is%20showing%20better%20economics%20and%20properties%20than%20red%20clay%20bricks%20and%20fly%20ash%20bricks%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20If%20the%20profits%20are%20translated%20to%20monetary%20value%2C%20then%20the%20income%20from%20wet%20cow%20dung%20can%20increase%20from%20the%20current%20value%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%201%20to%20over%20Rs%204%20per%20kilogram%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20a%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20IIT-Indore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGOBAiR%20can%20be%20added%20in%20concrete%2C%20bricks%2C%20tiles%20and%20blocks%2C%20to%20produce%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20sustainable%20building%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20using%20GOBAiR%20will%20be%20much%20more%20environmentally%20friendly%20and%20will%20help%20achieve%20more%20points%20in%20green%20building%20ratings%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20is%20presently%20working%20on%20developing%20a%20specifications%20table%20that%20the%20construction%20industry%20can%20use%20as%20a%20ready%20reference%20for%20adding%20GOBAiR%20in%20concrete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20is%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20IGBC%20for%20the%20Green%20Product%20Certification%20of%20building%20products%20made%