5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgujarat-man-went-to-drop-wife-at-station-got-locked-in-moving-train-read-hilarious-post-5362355%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fgujarat-man-went-to-drop-wife-at-station-got-locked-in-moving-train-read-hilarious-post-5362355%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Remain%20A%20Hero%26quot%3B%3A%20M%20Kharge%20As%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Retires%20From%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20will%20retire%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha%20tomorrow%2C%20ending%20his%2033-year-long%20stint.%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20wrote%20a%20heartfelt%20letter%20dedicated%20to%20the%2091-year-old's%20work%2C%20the%20policies%20he%20introduced%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20PM%20and%20finance%20minister%2C%20and%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20with%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20retirement%2C%20%26quot%3Ban%20era%20comes%20to%20an%20end%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BVery%20few%20people%20have%20accomplished%20as%20much%20as%20you%20for%20the%20nation%20and%20its%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20Mr%20Kharge%20expressed%20his%20gratitude%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh%20for%20his%20wisdom%20and%20guidance%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bprivilege%26quot%3B%20for%20him%20to%20serve%20under%20Singh's%20cabinet.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20you%20have%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20be%20available%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20despite%20personal%20inconveniences.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20party%20and%20I%20will%20always%20remain%20grateful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEven%20as%20you%20retire%20from%20active%20politics%2C%20I%20hope%20that%20you%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20wisdom%20and%20moral%20compass%20to%20the%20nation%20by%20speaking%20to%20the%20citizens%20of%20our%20country%20as%20often%20as%20possible.%20I%20wish%20you%20peace%2C%20health%20and%20happiness.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCongress%20President%20Shri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Kharge%3C%2Fa%3E%20writes%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ffq2nTbwXqE%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ffq2nTbwXqE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Congress%20(%40INCIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1775191840284950873%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppreciating%20the%20economic%20policies%20introduced%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20shown%20that%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20pursue%20economic%20policies%20that%20were%20equally%20beneficial%20to%20large%20groups%2C%20young%20entrepreneurs%2C%20small%20businesses%2C%20the%20salaried%20class%2C%20and%20the%20poor%20.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20your%20policies%2C%20India%20was%20able%20to%20lift%2027%20crore%20people%2C%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20poor%20people%20out%20of%20poverty%20in%20the%20world%20while%20you%20were%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Manmohan%20Singh%20will%20always%20remain%20%26quot%3Ba%20hero%20to%20the%20middle%20class%20and%20the%20aspirational%20youth%2C%20a%20leader%20and%20guide%20to%20the%20industrialists%20and%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20a%20benefactor%20to%20all%20those%20poor%20who%20were%20able%20to%20climb%20out%20of%20poverty%20due%20to%20your%20economic%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20praised%20Manmohan%20Singh%20for%20introducing%20the%20MGNREGA%20scheme%20and%20said%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20rural%20workers%20during%20times%20of%20crisis.%20%26quot%3BThe%20nation%20and%20particularly%20the%20rural%20population%20will%20remember%20you%20for%20ensuring%20that%20they%20can%20earn%20a%20living%20and%20live%20with%20self-respect%20through%20this%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20mentioned%20several%20achievements%20and%20key%20moments%20of%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20tenure%20as%20the%20PM%20and%20as%20finance%20minister.%20He%20appreciates%20him%20for%20pursuing%20the%20historic%20Indo-US%20Nuclear%20Deal%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20it%20meant%20putting%20your%20government%20at%20risk%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20nation's%20security.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20mentions%20remembering%20when%20former%20US%20President%20Obama%20said%20for%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20speaks%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20listens%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20we%20live%20in%20times%20that%20are%20largely%20shaped%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh.%20%26quot%3BThe%20economic%20prosperity%20and%20stability%20that%20we%20enjoy%20today%20is%20built%20on%20the%20foundations%20laid%20by%20you%20along%20with%20our%20former%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Shri%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20current%20set%20of%20leaders%20who%20have%20reaped%20the%20benefits%20of%20your%20work%20are%20reluctant%20to%20credit%20you%20due%20to%20political%20biases%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20attacking%20the%20ruling%20government.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20reforms%20done%20by%20the%20current%20government%20has%20its%20seed%20in%20the%20work%20initiated%20during%20the%20UPA%20government%20headed%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20nation%20misses%20the%20quiet%20yet%20strong%20dignity%20Manmohan%20Singh%20brought%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Par