ttps%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Frlcl5fsg_oyo-room_625x300_02_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-man-seeks-refuge-in-oyo-room-to-beat-the-heat-company-reacts-5361919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20individual%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20to%20address%20the%20rising%20temperature%20in%20Bengaluru%20which%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20pleasant%20climate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-man-seeks-refuge-in-oyo-room-to-beat-the-heat-company-reacts-5361919%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-man-seeks-refuge-in-oyo-room-to-beat-the-heat-company-reacts-5361919%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fbengaluru-man-seeks-refuge-in-oyo-room-to-beat-the-heat-company-reacts-5361919%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yoga%20In%20Space%3F%20Rakesh%20Sharma%20On%20Being%20The%20World's%20First%20'Antariksh%20Yogi'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20thought%20practising%20yoga%20was%20tough%2C%20try%20doing%20it%20in%20zero%20gravity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20the%20only%20person%20from%20India%20to%20have%20spent%20time%20in%20the%20final%20frontier%2C%20Wing%20Commander%20Rakesh%20Sharma%20also%20has%20the%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20first%20person%20to%20practise%20the%20ancient%20Indian%20discipline%20in%20space%2C%20making%20him%20the%20first%20'%3Cem%3EAntariksh%20Yogi'%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2040%20years%20after%20he%20blasted%20off%20into%20space%2C%20Wing%20Commander%20Sharma%20spoke%20to%20NDTV's%20Science%20Editor%20Pallava%20Bagla%20on%20using%20a%20special%20harness%20to%20do%20the%20'%3Cem%3Easanas'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(yoga%20positions)%2C%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20gravity%20and%20how%20the%20results%20of%20his%20yoga%20routine%20compared%20with%20the%20training%20regimen%20followed%20by%20Russian%20cosmonauts%20who%20were%20on%20the%20mission%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronaut%20said%20the%20yoga%20experiment%20was%20included%20in%20the%20mission%20brief%20of%20the%20Soyuz%20T-11%2C%20the%20sixth%20expedition%20to%20the%20Soviet%20Salyut%207%20space%20station%20which%20launched%20on%20April%203%2C%201984%2C%20because%20all%20spacefaring%20countries%20were%20looking%20for%20methods%20to%20avoid%20space%20sickness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20were%20various%20preparation%20methods...%20the%20one%20which%20the%20West%20followed%20and%20the%20one%20which%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20followed%20at%20that%20time.%20So%20here%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20find%20out%20if%20the%20yogic%20method%20of%20preparing%20space%20travellers%20to%20withstand%20the%20rigours%20of%20space%20would%20offer%20a%20different%2C%20viable%20alternative.%20Both%20Ravish%20sir%20(Ravish%20Malhotra%2C%20his%20backup%20on%20the%20mission)%20and%20I%20did%20yoga%20about%20three%20to%20four%20months%20before%20the%20launch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20pilot%20said%20they%20had%20stopped%20training%20as%20per%20the%20Russian%20regimen%20and%20the%20idea%20was%20to%20find%20out%20how%20well%20prepared%20they%20were%20compared%20to%20the%20cosmonauts%20in%20all%20phases%20-%20before%20the%20launch%2C%20in%20space%20and%20after%20they%20came%20back%20to%20Earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20did%20teach%20us%20a%20few%20lessons%20because%20doing%20yoga%20in%20space%20means%20that%20you%20are%20doing%20it%20in%20zero%20gravity.%20Whereas%20on%20Earth%2C%20when%20you%20are%20doing%20yoga%2C%20there%20is%20gravity.%20The%20tensions%20are%20missing%20in%20orbit.%20So%2C%20a%20harness%20was%20designed%20with%20elastic%20cords%20to%20replicate%20that%20gravity.%20But%2C%20then%2C%20even%20balancing%20yourself%20is%20a%20bit%20difficult.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20say%20that%20if%20a%20purist%20had%20seen%20us%20doing%20yoga%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20quite%20disappointed%2C%26quot%3B%20Wing%20Commander%20Sharma%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronaut%20said%20a%20lesson%20learnt%20was%20that%20if%20yoga%20is%20to%20be%20practised%20in%20space%2C%20a%20better%20harness%20is%20needed.%20On%20the%20results%20of%20the%20comparison%20between%20the%20yogic%20preparation%20and%20the%20regimen%20followed%20by%20the%20Russian%20cosmonauts%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnone%20the%20worse%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20one%20can%20at%20least%20say%20that%20preparation%20by%20the%20yogic%20system%20was%20not%20worse%20than%20what%20was%20being%20done.%20But%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20better%20would%20need%20a%20wider%20sample%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20would%20recommend%20the%20yoga%20regimen%20to%20India's%20four%20astronaut%20designates%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20programme%2C%20Wing%20Commander%20Sharma%20said%20it%20can%20happen%20during%20subsequent%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20would%20leave%20it%20to%20those%20who%20are%20getting%20the%20experiments%20together%20because%20time%20has%20passed.%20One%20thing%20that%20has%20not%20changed%20is%20the%20physiology%20of%20the%20human%20being.%20So%2C%20I%20guess%2C%20from%20that%20aspect%20it%20would%20remain%20relevant.%20But%20let%20them%20decide...I%20think%20for%20the%20first%20few%20flights%2C%20it's%20more%20important%20for%20us%20to%20prove%20the%20systems%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20reliable%20so%20that%20we%20can%20continue%20down%20this%20path.%20These%20experiments%20can%20happen%20at%20a%20later%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712076480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvv5opg6_rakesh-sharma-yoga_625x300_02_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22origi