eaders-swell-congress-bjp-ranks-ahead-of-polls-5361708%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-kcrs-leaders-swell-congress-bjp-ranks-ahead-of-polls-5361708%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-telangana-kcrs-leaders-swell-congress-bjp-ranks-ahead-of-polls-5361708%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency's%20Liquor%20Policy%20Kickback%20Charge%20In%20Court%2C%20%26quot%3BLies%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20spent%20Rs%2045%20crore%20on%20the%20election%20in%20Goa%20and%20there%20is%20enough%20evidence%20that%20party%20chief%20and%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20involved%20in%20money%20laundering%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20told%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20today%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20remarked%20on%20its%20failure%20to%20produce%20evidence%20of%20a%20money%20trail%20and%20gave%20bail%20to%20senior%20party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20AAP%20rubbed%20in%20the%20top%20court's%20comments%2C%20calling%20the%20agency's%20allegation%20a%20%26quot%3Blie%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ED%20just%20lies.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20no%20money%20trail%20was%20found%2C%20and%20no%20money%20was%20found.%20The%20ED%20could%20not%20provide%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20is%20working%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20BJP%2C%20which%20wants%20to%20topple%20Delhi%20government%20at%20any%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20AAP's%20statement%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Central%20investigation%20agency%20made%20its%20allegations%20on%20Goa%20official%2C%20including%20it%20in%20its%20response%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20challenge%20to%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20also%20demanded%20release%20as%20interim%20relief.%20The%20matter%20would%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20court%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20AAP%20the%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20generated%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Scam%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20ED%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20cash%20of%20Rs.%2045%20crore%20approx.%20has%20been%20utilised%20in%20the%20election%20campaign%20of%20AAP%20in%20Goa%20Assembly%20elections%202022%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20questioned%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20objections%2C%20arguing%20that%20he%20has%20waived%20his%20right%20to%20question%20his%20detention%20today%2C%20and%20cannot%20now%20be%20allowed%20to%20argue%20that%20it%20is%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20proper%20procedures%20under%20Section%2016%20of%20PMLA%20and%20Article%2022%20of%20the%20Constitution%20were%20strictly%20followed%20during%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20section%20empowers%20the%20ED%20to%20arrest%20anyone%20on%20basis%20of%20material%20in%20their%20possession%20that%20indicate%20s%2Fhe%20has%20committed%20an%20offence%20punishable%20under%20law.%20The%20agency%20is%20allowed%20to%20record%20its%20reasons%20for%20such%20belief%20in%20writing%2C%20with%20the%20grounds%20of%20arrest%20to%20be%20communicated%20to%20the%20accused%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20may%20be%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20plea%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20that%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20ED%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20material%20in%20possession%20that%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20belief%20of%20his%20guilt.%20The%20provisions%20of%20PMLA%20are%20being%20used%20to%20persecute%20and%20destroy%20the%20fabric%20of%20the%20democratic%20and%20federal%20structures%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20attempt%20is%20to%20decimate%20a%20political%20party%20and%20topple%20an%20elected%20government%20of%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20bail%20to%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20asking%20why%20he%20had%20been%20jailed%20for%20over%20six%20months%20without%20a%20trial%20or%20recovery%20of%20alleged%20bribe%20of%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20questioned%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%20to%20support%20ED's%20claim%20that%20the%20party%20received%20Rs%20600%20crore%20in%20bribe.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20has%20been%20recovered...%20there%20is%20no%20trace%20(of%20money%20allegedly%20received%20by%20the%20AAP%20as%20bribes%20for%20allotting%20liquor%20licences%20to%20the%20'South%20Group')%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20asked%20where%20the%20money%20trail%20was.%20A%20search%20for%20that%20money%20trail%20has%20been%20on%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20Today%2C%20when%20the%20court%20asked%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20no%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20minister%20and%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20Atishi%20told%20reporters%20after%20Sanjay%20Singh%20got%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712074560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fotsbh9us_arvind-kejriwal-pti_625x300_02_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-makes-liquor-policy-kickback-charge-official-aap-says-lies-5361430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20spent%20Rs%2045%20crore%20on%20the%20election%20in%20Goa%20and%20there%20is%20enough%20evidence%20that%20party%20chief%20and%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20involved%20in%20money%20laundering%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20told%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20today%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-makes-liquor-policy-kickback-charge-official-aap-says-lies-5361430%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-makes-liquor-policy-kickback-charge-official-aap-says-lies-5361430%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-makes-liquor-policy-kickback-charge-official-aap-says-lies-5361430%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20iOS%2018%3A%20Compatible%20Devices%2C%20New%20Features%2C%20Key%20Details%20And%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple's%202024%20Worldwide%20Developers%20Conference%20(WWDC)%20is%20just%20around%20the%20corner.%20Slated%20for%20June%2C%20the%20conference%20usually%20centres%20around%20iOS%20updates%20rather%20than%20new%20hardware.%20This%20year%2C%20among%20the%20most%20anticipated%20announcements%2C%20is%20the%20debut%20of%20iOS%2018%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20most%20significant%20software%20update%20for%20the%20iPhone%20that%20the%20tech%20giant%20has%20shipped%20in%20years.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ECNET%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20new%20iOS%2018%20will%20revamp%20the%20iPhone%20experience%20with%20four%20new%20artificial%20intelligence-powered%20features%2C%20including%20large%20language%20models%20(LLMS)%20and%20a%20generative%20AI%20app%20called%20iWork.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20never%20discusses%20products%20before%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20announce%20them.%20However%2C%20Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20recently%20teased%20that%20the%20company%20has%20big%20plans%20regarding%20generative%20AI.%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20just%20say%20that%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20for%20Apple%20with%20GenAI%20and%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20most%20recent%20earnings%20call%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Ftech%2Fmobile%2Fwhy-ios-18-could-be-a-bigger-deal-than-the-iphone-16%2F%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%