20who%20took%20power%20in%202022%20after%20her%20predecessor%20was%20impeached%20for%20illegally%20trying%20to%20shutter%20congress%2C%20saw%20the%20beginning%20of%20her%20term%20marked%20by%20protests%20and%20ensuing%20crackdown%20that%20left%20dozens%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20widespread%20calls%20for%20her%20resignation%20or%20to%20bring%20forward%20elections%2C%20Dina%20Boluarte%20survived%20but%20is%20now%20facing%20renewed%20calls%20to%20step%20down%20over%20the%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20televised%20address%20to%20the%20nation%20Dina%20Boluarte%20called%20the%20raid%20%26quot%3Babusive%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20she%20would%20serve%20her%20term%20until%202026.%20Congress%20has%20already%20taken%20initial%20steps%20to%20impeach%20Boluarte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20Rolex%20Scandal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20a%20popular%20political%20Youtube%20show%20%26quot%3BLa%20Encerrona%26quot%3B%20reviewed%20thousands%20of%20photos%20of%20Dina%20Boluarte%20and%20found%20she%20wore%20a%20number%20of%20Rolex%20watches%20worth%20between%20%2414%2C000%20and%20%2425%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2018%2C%20the%20Peru's%20prosecutor's%20office%20announced%20%26quot%3Bpreliminary%20proceedings%26quot%3B%20against%20Dina%20Boluarte%20for%20alleged%20%26quot%3Billicit%20enrichment%26quot%3B%20and%20failure%20to%20declare%20ownership%20of%20the%20expensive%20Rolex%20watches%20in%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20duting%20the%20raid%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20prosecutors%20and%20police%20arrived%20at%20Dina%20Boluarte's%20house%20near%20midnight%20on%20Good%20Friday%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20search%20warrant%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20they%20had%20requested%20the%20watches%20from%20Dina%20Boluarte%20but%20they%20had%20not%20been%20handed%20in%20and%20the%20raid%20produced%20%26quot%3Belements%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20outlets%20published%20documents%20from%20the%20raid%20showing%20at%20least%20one%20Rolex%20watch%2C%20a%20Datejust%2036%20model%20with%20a%20purchase%20date%20of%20July%208%2C%202023.%20A%20similar%20model%20on%20Rolex's%20website%20costs%20at%20least%20%2414%2C800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20lower-priced%20watches%20from%20other%20brands%20were%20found%20in%20the%20Government%20Palace%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media%20reports.%20Dina%20Boluarte's%20salary%20as%20president%20is%20about%20%244%2C200%20with%20expenses%20and%20housing%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDina%20Boluarte's%20defense%20had%20asked%20the%20prosecutor%20to%20postpone%20the%20president's%20testimony%2C%20but%20are%20now%20requesting%20she%20give%20a%20statement%20Friday%20April%205%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20turbulence%26quot%3B%20the%20case%20is%20causing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMostly%20left-wing%20opposition%20legislators%2C%20presented%20a%20motion%20in%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20to%20begin%20Dina%20Boluarte's%20impeachment%20for%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%20moral%20incapacity%26quot%3B.%20Only%2026%20of%20130%20legislators%20are%20needed%20to%20start%20the%20process%2C%2052%20votes%20are%20needed%20to%20debate%20the%20impeachment%20in%20Congress%20and%2087%20are%20needed%20to%20impeach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDina%20Boluarte%20has%20already%20survived%20two%20attempts%20to%20start%20impeachment%20proceedings%20but%20both%20failed%20to%20receive%2052%20votes%20to%20proceed.%20Impeachment%20is%20unlikely%20since%20right-wing%20legislators%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20congress%20and%20support%20Dina%20Boluarte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20of%20Dina%20Boluarte's%20ministers%2C%20including%20the%20interior%20minister%2C%20have%20resigned%20on%20Monday%20over%20the%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGustavo%20Adrianzen%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20prime%20minister%20in%20March%2C%20must%20be%20confirmed%20by%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20if%20he%20fails%20the%20vote%20of%20confidence%2C%20Dina%20Boluarte's%20entire%20cabinet%20must%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20Peru's%20other%20Presidents%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeru's%20politics%20are%20highly%20polarized%20and%20the%20constitution%20allows%20presidents%20to%20be%20impeached%20for%20%26quot%3Bmoral%20incapacity%26quot%3B%20a%20subjective%20measure%20that's%20been%20used%20to%20impeach%20several%20former%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20high-ranking%20officials%20or%20former%20Peruvian%20presidents%20have%20been%20investigated%20by%20the%20prosecution%20or%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20corruption%20cases%20in%20the%20last%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20elected%20in%202016%2C%20Pedro%20Pablo%20Kuczynski%20resigned%20prior%20to%20a%20likely%20conviction%20after%20being%20succesfuly%20impeached%20in%202018%20following%20a%20corruption%20scandal.%20His%20vice%20president%2C%20Martin%20Vizcarra%2C%20then%20took%20over%20but%20was%20also%20impeached%20for%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%20moral%20incapacity%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20corruption%20charges%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20Manuel%20Merino%20was%20president%20for%20just%20five%20days%2C%20resigning%20after%20two%20protest%20deaths%20in%20Lima.%20Francisco%20Sagasti%20then%20took%20power%20for%20a%20year%20until%20leftists%20outsider%20Pedro%20Castillo%20was%20elected%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECastillo%20was%20impeached%20in%20December%20for%20trying%20to%20shutter%20congress.%20Castillo%20is%20now%20jailed%20in%20the%20same%20prison%20as%20another%20former%20president%20Alejandro%20Toledo.%20They%20shared%20the%20prison%20with%20former%20President%20Alberto%20Fujimori%20who%20was%20released%20last%20December%20after%20a%20pardon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20bee