mar%20Kait%20and%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20estranged%20couple%20got%20married%20in%20April%202008%20and%20a%20son%20was%20born%20to%20them%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20plea%2C%20Kunal%20Kapur%2C%20who%20was%20a%20judge%20in%20the%20television%20show%20%26quot%3BMaster%20Chef%26quot%3B%2C%20accused%20his%20wife%20of%20never%20respecting%20his%20parents%20and%20humiliating%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20woman%20accused%20him%20of%20making%20false%20allegations%20to%20mislead%20the%20court%20and%20said%20she%20always%20tried%20to%20communicate%20with%20her%20husband%20like%20a%20loving%20spouse%20and%20was%20loyal%20towards%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20kept%20her%20in%20the%20dark%20and%20concocted%20fabricated%20stories%20to%20obtain%20divorce%2C%20she%20had%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20though%20discords%20are%20an%20inevitable%20part%20of%20every%20marriage%2C%20when%20such%20conflicts%20take%20the%20form%20of%20disrespect%20and%20inconsideration%20towards%20a%20spouse%2C%20the%20marriage%20itself%20loses%20its%20sanctity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20relevant%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20within%20two%20years%20of%20marriage%2C%20the%20appellant%20has%20established%20himself%20as%20a%20celebrity%20chef%2C%20which%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20his%20hard%20work%20and%20determination....%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20the%20aforesaid%20facts%2C%20it%20is%20only%20prudent%20to%20observe%20that%20these%20are%20mere%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20respondent%20to%20disrepute%20the%20appellant%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20court%20and%20such%20unsubstantiated%20claims%20have%20the%20effect%20on%20one's%20reputation%20and%20therefore%2C%20amounts%20to%20cruelty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712067600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F1q1m88q_kunal-kapur_625x300_01_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-grants-divorce-to-chef-kunal-kapur-over-cruelty-by-wife-5360952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20granted%20divorce%20to%20celebrity%20chef%20Kunal%20Kapur%20on%20Tuesday%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20cruelty%20meted%20out%20to%20him%20by%20his%20estranged%20wife%2C%20saying%20the%20woman's%20conduct%20towards%20him%20was%20devoid%20of%20dignity%20and%20empathy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-grants-divorce-to-chef-kunal-kapur-over-cruelty-by-wife-5360952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-grants-divorce-to-chef-kunal-kapur-over-cruelty-by-wife-5360952%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-court-grants-divorce-to-chef-kunal-kapur-over-cruelty-by-wife-5360952%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20were%20the%20seven%20aid%20workers%20killed%20in%20Gaza%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712067598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10064%2Fproduction%2F_133063656_26f550eabf8e1fe9741e76e8f2d6dcedcbfa93530_0_5120_28801000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68711282%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seven%20aid%20workers%2C%20including%20foreign%20nationals%2C%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20central%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1641%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68711282%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68711282.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68711282.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%20backs%20author%20JK%20Rowling%20over%20Scottish%20hate%20crime%20law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712067395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108980781%2Cimgsize-956627.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-backs-author-jk-rowling-over-scottish-hate-crime-law%2Farticleshow%2F108980588.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108980588.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-backs-author-jk-rowling-over-scottish-hate-crime-law%2Farticleshow%2F108980588.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-backs-author-jk-rowling-over-scottish-hate-crime-law%2Famp_articleshow%2F108980588.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-backs-author-jk-rowling-over-scottish-hate-crime-law%2Famp_articleshow%2F108980588.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPioneering%20Gaganyatri%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%20Chief%20Applauds%20India's%20Only%20Astronaut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBharat%20is%20still%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Esaare%20jahan%20se%20accha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(best%20in%20the%20world)%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20country's%20very%20first%20cosmonaut%20Rakesh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20is%20celebrating%20the%2040th%20anniversary%20of%20that%20historic%20flight.%20Closely%20connected%20to%20the%20country's%20fresh%20effort%20to%20put%20four%20cosmonauts%20in%20space%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20who%20is%20now%2075%20years%20old%2C%20said%20he%20would%20love%20to%20take%20another%20flight%2C%20but%20only%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btourist%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThere%20was%20too%20much%20work.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20put%20my%20nose%20on%20the%20window%20(this%20time)%20and%20enjoy%20the%20sights%20of%20Mother%20Earth%20from%20space%2C''%20he%20told%20NDTV's%20Science%20Editor%20Pallava%20Bagla%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnToday%2C%20as%20India%20is%20preparing%20for%20its%20maiden%20human%20space%20flight%20as%20part%20of%20Mission%20Gaganyaan%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20or%20ISRO%20is%20also%20looking%20at%20that%20golden%20moment%2040%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSquadron%20Leader%20Rakesh%20Sharma's%20journey%20to%20space%20not%20only%20inspired%20Bharat%20but%20also%20symbolized%20the%20boundless%20potential%20of%20human%20endeavour%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20S%20Somanath%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20space%20research%20organisation%2C%20who%20was%2021%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20this%2040th%20anniversary%20of%20historic%20space%20flight%2C%20let%20us%20take%20a%20moment%20to%20honour%20his%20remarkable%20achievement%20and%20the%20indelible%20mark%20he%20left%20on%20Indian%20space%20exploration%2C'%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20was%20made%20on%20April%203%2C%201984%2C%20when%20Squadron%20Leader%20Rakesh%20Sharma%20lifted%20off%20on%20a%20Soviet%20rocket%20and%20became%20India's%20first%20%26quot%3BGaganyatri%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20term%20the%20country%20has%20made%20official.%20He%20stayed%20on%20the%20Soviet%20space%20station%20for%207%20days%20and%2021%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20conversation%20with%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20--beamed%20into%20every%20house%20by%20Doordarshan%20--%20had%20thrilled%20the%20nation.%20To%20her%20question%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EUpar%20se%20Bharat%20kaisa%20lag%20raha%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(How%20does%20India%20look%20from%20up%20there)%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20responded%20with%20the%20famous%20line%20penned%20by%20Alama%20Iqbal%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESaare%20jahan%20se%20accha%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Sharma%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20the%20line%20was%20not%20rehearsed%20at%20all.%20He%20used%20to%20sing%20the%20legendary%20song%20in%20school%20so%20it%20came%20naturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20is%20now%20hoping%20to%20send%20one%20of%20four%20astronaut%20designates%20into%20space%20from%20Sriharikota%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Mission%20Gaganyaan.%20The%20rocket%20would%20be%20Indian%20and%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20time%2C%20the%20countdown%20will%20be%20ours%20too%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnGroup%20Captain%20Ravish%20Malhotra%2C%20who%20trained%20alongside%20Mr%20Sharma%20and%20was%20a%20standby%20cosmonaut%2C%20never%20flew%20into%20space.%20Now%2081%20years%20old%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20help%20create%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20vibrant%20aerospace%20companies%20--%20the%20Dynamatic%20Technologies%20in%20Bengaluru.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpeaking%20of%20him%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20of%20being%20selected%20to%20go%20up%20in%20space.%20I%20wish%20to%20emphasize%20that%20it%20was%20sheer%20good%20fortune%20because%20between%20my%20colleague%20Ravish%20Sir%20and%20myself%2C%20I%20can%20lay%20claim%20to%20no%20special%20quality%20that%20was%20present%20only%20in%20me%20and%20not%20him%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Sharma%20now%20helps%20ISRO%20train%20the%20four%20astronaut%20designates%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20Mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20had%20trained%20in%20yoga%20before%20his%20flight%20and%20performed%20it%20while%20in%20the%20near%20zero%20gravity%20condition.%20The%20practice%20had%20earned%20him%20the%20moniker%20%26quot%3BWorld's%20first%20Antriksh%20Yogi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPurists%20will%20find%20the%20yoga%20I%20performed%20as%20naive.%20But%20doing%20it%20in%20weightless%20condition%20is%20not%20easy%20and%20a%20quality%20harness%20is%20required%20to%20hold%20the%20Yogi%20in%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20ISRO%20said%20yoga%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20routine%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BFabulous%20four%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20Gaganyatri%20designates%20are%20often%20called.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Somanath%20said%20Mr%20Sharma%20has%20been%20the%20%26quot%3Bsupporter%2C%20promoter%20and%20advisor%20for%20development%20of%20Gaganyaan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20continues%20to%20support%20ISRO%20in%20many%20ways%20to%20develop%20the%20human%20space%20flight%20capability.%20He%20remains%20a%20pioneering%20Gaganyatri%20for%20India%2C%20as%20the%20four%20candidates%20follow%20in%20his%20footsteps%20as%20part%20of%20Mission%20Gaganyaan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Sharma%20said%20he%20eagerly%20awaits%20the%20day%20when%20he%20will%20get%20the%20company%20of%20an%20Indian%20in%20that%20elite%20club%20of%20%26quot%3BUniverse%20Gazers%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712067180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3jk369ng_rakesh-sharma_625x300_27_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpioneering-gaganyatri-isro-chief-applauds-indias-only-astronaut-5360851%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bharat%20is%20still%20%26quot%3Bsaare%20jahan%20se%20accha%20(best%20in%20the%20world)%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20country's%20very%20first%20cosmonaut%20Rakesh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20is%20celebrating%20the%2040th%20anniversary%20of%20that%20historic%20flight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpi