moved%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20she%20was%20disheartened%20to%20witness%20ecological%20degradation.%20Having%20spent%20her%20childhood%20enjoying%20the%20shade%20of%20trees%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20raise%20her%20daughter%20in%20an%20environment%20closer%20to%20nature.%20This%20motivated%20her%20to%20create%20this%20organic%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20one%20day%2C%20she%20saw%20a%20small%20caterpillar%20eating%20a%20leaf%20from%20one%20of%20her%20plants.%20And%20after%20a%20few%20days%2C%20she%20saw%20that%20this%20caterpillar%20had%20transformed%20into%20a%20beautiful%20butterfly.%20After%20that%20incident%2C%20she%20became%20so%20fond%20of%20butterflies%20that%20she%20started%20reading%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20newfound%20passion%20led%20her%20to%20create%20a%20small%20ecosystem%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127454%2Fkerala-butterfly-parks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erear%20butterflies%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20her%20home%20on%20the%2013th%20floor.%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20she%20claims%20to%20have%20nurtured%20over%205%2C000%20butterflies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Priyanka%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712066370000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fbutterfly-1712053091.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346252%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20to%20grow%20a%20garden%20that%20attracts%20butterflies%3F%20Mumbai-based%20Priyanka%20Singh%20has%20turned%20her%20balcony%20into%20a%20haven%20for%20over%205%2C000%20butterflies%20so%20far.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20the%20journey%20that%20led%20her%20to%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346252%2Fgarden-attracting-butterflied-mumbai-priyanka-singh-endangered-