ng%20class.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98pice%E2%80%99%20borrows%20from%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98paisa%E2%80%99%20considered%20the%20lowest%20denomination%20in%20Indian%20currency.%20The%20%3Cem%3Epice%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20a%20monetary%20unit%20of%20British%20India%20equivalent%20to%20one-quarter%20of%20an%20anna.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261622%2Fwhats-bitter-beloved-of-bengalis-shukto-a-culinary-gem-with-a-story-to-tell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20light%20on%20the%20pocket%2C%20an%20advantage%20during%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Independence%20movement%20as%20Indians%20struggled%20with%20migrations%2C%20loss%20of%20business%2C%20and%20limited%20food%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20food%20historian%20Tanushree%20Bhowmik%20emphasised%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EPice%3C%2Fem%3E%20hotels%20stand%20out%20as%20the%20first%20commercial%20indigenous%20eating%20places%20in%20the%20city.%20People%20moved%20from%20rural%20to%20urban%20areas%20as%20the%20economy%20shifted%20from%20agrarian%20to%20industrial%2C%20and%20these%20hotels%20sprung%20up%20to%20meet%20its%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20hearsay%20that%20even%20at%20a%20time%20when%20sustainability%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20buzzword%20that%20it%20is%20today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263077%2Fbest-food-kolkata-famous-pice-hotels-history-british-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20%3Cem%3Epice%3C%2Fem%3E%20hotels%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20acing%20the%20game.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20to%20keep%20operating%20costs%20low%20while%20continuing%20to%20maintain%20a%20profitable%20business%2C%20these%20hotels%20toyed%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20seasonal%20eating%20while%20prioritising%20fresh%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20