eticulously%20planned%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1705381%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%2520has%2520approved%2Con%252017th%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202021%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20amend%20the%20MTP%20Act%201971.%20The%20Bill%20was%20approved%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20enhanced%20the%20upper%20gestation%20limit%20from%2020%20to%2024%20weeks%20for%20special%20categories%20of%20women%20which%20will%20be%20defined%20in%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20Act.%20It%20would%20include%20survivors%20of%20rape%2C%20victims%20of%20incest%2C%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20women%20such%20as%20disabled%20women%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20again%20an%20arbitrary%20limit%2C%2024%20weeks%20is%20still%20a%20pretty%20decent%20time%20frame%20to%20detect%20abnormalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20his%20patients%2C%20this%20judgement%20has%20been%20extremely%20satisfying%20for%20Dr%20Nikhil%20personally%2C%20who%20has%20fought%20multiple%20challenges%20and%20threats%20in%20various%20forms%20in%20his%2014-year%20crusade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20we%20see%20families%20starting%20with%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20children.%20We%20become%20a%20part%20of%20these%20units%20as%20they%20remember%20us%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20get%2030%20such%20cases%20every%20month.%20But%20when%20you%20are%20able%20to%20contribute%20towards%20a%20larger%20policy%20change%2C%20you%20are%20able%20to%20impact%20lakhs%20and%20crores%20of%20lives%20known%20and%20unknown%20to%20you.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20whole%20new%20level%20of%20satisfaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pa