%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20the%20place%20is%20perfect%20for%20stargazing.%20The%20skies%20on%20a%20clear%20night%20are%20full%20of%20beautiful%20stars%20that%20our%20guests%20can%20enjoy%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20attraction%20of%20the%20place%20is%20its%20delicious%20food.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20the%20guests%20to%20experience%20every%20cuisine%20they%20want%20when%20they%20visit%20Himalaica.%20So%20we%20hired%20chefs%20who%20can%20cook%20anything%20you%20want%20at%20your%20command%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSay%20you%20want%20to%20eat%20something%20from%20Italian%20cuisine%20or%20French%20cuisine%2C%20you%20can%20ask%20the%20chefs%20to%20cook%20those%20dishes%20for%20you.%20We%20also%20offer%20classes%20if%20the%20guests%20want%20to%20learn%20to%20cook%20any%20particular%20dish%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20has%20hosted%20countless%20guests%20at%20the%20property%20so%20far.%20The%20common%20review%20that%20the%20couple%20gets%20from%20their%20guests%20is%20how%20the%20property%20feels%20like%20home%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCZjivJ3MfCo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCZjivJ3MfCo%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%