0so%20I%20lived%20with%20my%20driver%20who%20was%20a%20local%20in%20Bera.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20used%20to%20make%20fun%20of%20me%20saying%20that%20I%20was%20living%20with%20my%20driver.%20But%20someone%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20mining%20project%20and%20I%20was%20very%20passionate%20about%20it.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F36889%2Finternational-day-of-snow-leopard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20agenda%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20very%20clear.%20I%20thought%2C%20if%20nobody%20does%20it%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20observation%20on%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20part%20has%20been%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20locals%20towards%20the%20leopards.%20Once%20frightened%20about%20leopard%20attacks%2C%20he%20says%20the%20locals%20(aside%20from%20the%20Rabari%20community)%20would%20poison%20the%20beasts.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20due%20to%20the%20tourism%20model%20in%20Bera%2C%20every%20villager%20is%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20associated%20with%20it.%20Since%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20tourism%20here%20is%20safaris%20to%20see%20the%20leopard%2C%20they%20understand%20how%20important%20the%20animal%20is%20for%20their%20welfare.%20Today%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F12694%2Fvanamitra-suresh-conserve-wildlife-india-leopards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehumans%20and%20leopards%20coexist%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconservation-1-1710483355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20has%20seven%20eco%20friendly%20cottages%20where%20people%20can%20st