400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20the%20best%20homestays%20in%20Kanyakumari%3F%20Rajchandar%20Padmanaban%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Naga%20Jeyalakshmi%2C%20built%20Muthunandhini%20Palace%20as%20a%20heritage%20home%20where%20sustainability%20meets%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20traditional%20architecture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345629%2Fmuthunandhini-palace-kanyakumari-ecofriendly-homestay-chettinad-architecture-tamil-nadu-travel-destination%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98We%20Should%20Experiment%E2%80%99%3A%20Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Switch%20From%20Wheat%20to%20Turmeric%20Doubled%20Her%20Income%20to%20Rs%2012%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELocated%20on%20the%20bank%20of%20the%20Narmada%20river%2C%20Narmadapuram%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20fertile%20black%20soil%20that%20yields%20high-quality%20wheat.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20place%20is%20said%20to%20be%20competing%20with%20the%20entire%20state%20of%20Punjab%20for%20wheat%20production.%20With%20good%20canal%20irrigation%20facilities%2C%20the%20farmers%2C%20however%2C%20also%20cultivate%20crops%20of%20soybean%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20gram%2C%20and%20paddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrying%20something%20new%2C%20a%20progressive%20farmer%20Kanchan%20Verma%20ventured%20into%20turmeric%20farming%20in%20the%20division.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20did%20not%20face%20any%20losses%20cultivating%20traditional%20crops%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20new%20crops%20for%20better%20returns.%20As%20a%20farmer%2C%20we%20should%20keep%20experimenting%20in%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20cultivating%20traditional%20crops%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20in%20an%20acre.%20Wh